<h2>Thanks for signing up!</h2>

<p>In order to confirm your email address, we've just sent an email to: <code class="email"><%= current_person.email %></code> <span class="help">(Incorrect address? Please <%= link_to('fix it in your profile', edit_person_path(current_person))%>)</span></p>

